node.text:
I’m on a mission to help the low income community that I grew up in - NewHolly, Seattle by raising funds to build a brand new soccer field and supportive programs and resources for the community with my friends at @ravefound & @soundersfc.

Here’s what you’ll get when you donate these amounts:

➡️ $10,000 Donation: Group Hangout with Thach For A Day (2 Group separate sessions of 10 People - Limited to 20 People)
1. Create a Personalized Road Map To Wealth ($5000)
2. Tour Thach’s Real Estate Projects($2000)
3. Meet The Team and Q&A ($1500)
4. Pick Thach’s Brain - Q&A ($7500)
5. Goodie Bag - New Merch ($500)
6. Ride In The BRRRR Machine

➡️ $20,000 Donation: 1-on-1 with Thach For A Day (Limited to 10 People)
*Everything In the $10K Donation PLUS*
7. Wholesale Mentorship Course ($2,000)
8. 2 Weekly Jumpstart Coaching Calls Live For 1 Year ($2400 value) - *not 6 months*
9. Spend Time with Thach Personally 1-on-1 for One Day And Ride In The BRRRR Machine ($15,000 value /Priceless)

LINK IN BIO!!! (side note: any amount of donation helps as well)

node.title: How To Get 1-on-1 Mentorship From Thach Nguyen

I’m on a mission to help the low income community that I grew up in - NewHolly, Seattle by raising funds to build a brand new soccer field and supportive programs and resources for the community with my friends at @ravefound & @soundersfc.
